<section class="ogm_s10 smSpace gradientS8"><div class="container h-100">
<div class="text-space center space-cont"><h3 class="hds1 tc sub_spc">FAQ</h3> </div>

<div class="accordion accordion-s1 accordion_ogm_s10">
<div class="accordion-item">
<h3 class="accordion-item-heading">What is Cloud TV OS?</h3>
<div class="accordion-content"><p>Cloud TV OS is a certified operating system for Smart TVs and Set-Top Boxes. Cloud TV OS provides OTT Apps, Free Live TV Channels, App Store, Content Recommendations, and more functionalities tailored for an excellent television experience. Powering more than 150+ TV brands and 22+ OEMs, Cloud TV is the leading Smart TV OS built for Indian Smart TV manufacturers, brands, and consumers.</p></div>
</div>

<div class="accordion-item">
<h3 class="accordion-item-heading">What are the features of Cloud TV OS?</h3>
<div class="accordion-content"><p>Cloud TV OS brings the latest features and enables its users to make the most of their TVs. Some of the features are:</p>
<ul class="inner_faq">
<li>
    <p>•
        <span>Official Apps:</span> Cloud TV OS supports a wide range of applications in the Cloud TV App Store. This includes popular streaming platforms like Prime Video, Disney+ Hotstar, SonyLiv, JioCinema, SunNXT, VOOT & many more. Users can download and install popular streaming apps, music apps, productivity apps, and a variety of games optimized for the Cloud TV platform.
    </p>
</li>
<li>
    <p>•
        <span>Free Live TV Streaming:</span> Cloud TV Channels gives you access to 250+ Live TV Channels at no cost!
    </p>
</li>
<li>
    <p>•
        <span>Content Recommendations:</span> Cloud TV OS brings a wide range of content from popular services such as Amazon Prime Video, Disney+ Hotstar, SonyLIV, Zee5, JioCinema, Voot and many others. It provides access to a vast library of Movies, TV shows, Live TV Channels, and other video content available for free or subscription.
    </p>
</li>
<li>
    <p>•
        <span>Voice Control:</span> Cloud TV OS integrates with Cloud TV’s voice assistant, enabling users to control their Cloud TV devices using voice commands. Users can search for content, control playback, adjust volume, open apps, switch between sources, and more.
    </p>
</li>
<li>
    <p>•
        <span>Screen Mirroring:</span> Cloud TV OS supports screen mirroring and casting from compatible devices, allowing users to mirror their smartphone, tablet, or computer screens on their Cloud TV devices.
    </p>
</li>
<li>
    <p>•
        <span>And More:</span> Check out all the features in detail <a href="#">here</a>.
    </p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div class="accordion-item">
<h3 class="accordion-item-heading">What are the prerequisites to embed Cloud TV OS on my devices?</h3>
<div class="accordion-content">
<ul class="inner_faq">
<li>
    <p>•
        <span>Technical Integration:</span> With a wide range of hardware support, integrating Cloud TV on your hardware is a breeze. Cloud TV can support most open-market AOSP-based SoC or PCBs which can be for 2K or 4K TVs. Cloud TV can support low-end affordable hardware or even high-end hardware.
    </p>
</li> 
<li>
    <p>•
        <span>Partner with Cloud TV OS:</span> Contact our partnerships team to express your interest in manufacturing a TV with Cloud TV OS. They will provide you with the necessary information and guidelines. You can reach us at <a href="mailto:contact@cloudtvos.com">contact@cloudtvos.com</a>
    </p>
</li> 
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<!-- hide div -->
